{
  "texts": [
    "To identify patients from our cohort who were experiencing housing instability (\"preliminary positive class\"), we searched for patients who had either a SNOMED code for housing instability (Supplementary Table S1) or a matching string for the word \"homeless\" in one or more of their free-text notes (n=13,024).",
    "Patients who did not meet these criteria were considered in the \"preliminary negative class\" (n=359,184) (Fig. 1).",
    "Fig. 1: Cohort selection and experimental design.",
    "*Pregnant patients were selected as previously described 32.",
    "Patients used for prompt engineering (100) and patients used for tagging (795) did not overlap."
  ]
}